                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>\n                                                  <sic>Pittsburg</sic>\n                                        </placeName>\n                                        <date>August 9<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>to the <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Dear sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">I take the liberty to communicate<lb/> to you the\n                                        proceedings of our last meeting (yesterday) Kahl\n                                                  Staray=<lb/>themajim<add>?</add>\n                                        <persName>Mr A. Fink</persName> has been elected\n                                                  <sic>Presitent</sic>. <persName role=\"author\">N.\n                                                  Gallinger</persName> secret.<lb/>\n                                        <persName>I. Morgenstern</persName> Tres. By this meeting\n                                        all our members (except two<lb/> have not been present) by\n                                        their own free will bound themself<lb/> to <sic>atent</sic>\n                                        regular divine service Every <date>Shabath</date> &amp; Holy\n                                        days or<lb/> be fined one dollar for each missing, as our\n                                        Kohl has been<lb/>\n                                        <sic>organist</sic> nearly five years but has not\n                                                  <sic>ingreased</sic> we only<lb/> number 15\n                                        members and have a <sic>yerly</sic> expense of about 450\n                                        Dollars<lb/> but still we get along so far <sic>exept</sic>\n                                        could very seldom get<lb/> minian on <date>Shabath</date>\n                                        but now by our determination with the<lb/> help of God will\n                                        have regular services on all <sic>occations</sic>\n                                        <persName>Mr. Salshath<add>?</add></persName><lb/> is our\n                                        chasan shodet &amp; teacher we have a burring Ground\n                                        and<lb/> have a fine <sic>larg</sic> &amp;\n                                                  <sic>compfortibel</sic> Rooms two <add>ספרים</add>\n                                        one belongs to<lb/> Kohl and the room well <sic>fixt</sic>\n                                        up for our <sic>Sinagoge</sic> we have<lb/> only 14 members\n                                        although <sic>ther</sic> are over thirty Jewish\n                                        Families<lb/> in this city <sic>ther</sic> is a other Kohl\n                                        here <sic>wich</sic> calls themselves Polish<lb/> they have\n                                        as I can judge about 8 or 9 members they would<lb/> not join\n                                        use because we <sic>wand</sic> them to pay as much<lb/>\n                                        towards the expenses as the members of our Kohl pay but<lb/>\n                                        we got along so far and I hope we will get along\n                                        further<lb/> we have <sic>severall</sic> Polish members in\n                                        our Kohl, they the Polish Kohl have <sic>injourd</sic><lb/>\n                                        us and tried to insure us <del>for</del> since they are here\n                                        on<lb/> every <date>rosh hasona</date> &amp;\n                                                  <date>Kipur</date>\n                                        <sic>the</sic> have <sic>organised</sic> a minian<lb/> for\n                                                  <sic>themsef</sic> and <del>got</del> trid all\n                                        means to get every stranger<lb/> away from our\n                                                  <sic>sinagoge</sic></p>\n                              "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3js9ht9m/canvas/p1"
